targets.query:
from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] =~ /\b${devices:regex}\b/)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "BMSmaxPackTemperature" or r["_field"] == "VCFRONT_tempAmbient" or r["_field"] == "DIR_oilPumpFluidT")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)
  |> yield(name: "mean")
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT * FROM $__database.$__table 
WHERE  measure_name = 'ActualVehicleSpeed'
--      AND (time between ago(15m) and now())
 and time between from_iso8601_timestamp('${__from:date:iso}') and from_iso8601_timestamp('${__to:date:iso}')
ORDER BY time Desc Limit 1
